---
import HomePanel from './HomePanel.astro';
import SectionRule from './SectionRule.astro';
---

<HomePanel id="industries" screenLabel="Industries">
  <SectionRule num="01" left="Industries" right="Where planning gets hard" />
  <div class="section-head reveal">
    <h2 class="display">Different industries.<br /><span class="accent">The same need for clarity.</span></h2>
    <p>Demand planning is difficult in different ways depending on the environment.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="ind-grid ind-grid--panel" style="margin-top:34px">
    <div class="ind reveal" data-delay="1">
      <div class="ind-vis"><svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none"><rect x="22" y="8" width="20" height="34" rx="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M22 24h20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M32 42v8M24 54h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
      <div><span class="mono-tag">Pharma</span><h3>Pharma</h3><p>Tight regulation and long lead times make demand swings expensive.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="ind reveal" data-delay="2">
      <div class="ind-vis"><svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none"><circle cx="22" cy="28" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="42" cy="40" r="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M22 16v-4M22 44v4M10 28H6M34 28h4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
      <div><span class="mono-tag">Manufacturing</span><h3>Manufacturing</h3><p>Capacity limits mean a forecast miss ripples into production.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="ind reveal" data-delay="1">
      <div class="ind-vis"><svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none"><path d="M34 8L18 36h12l-2 20 18-30H32z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
      <div><span class="mono-tag">Energy</span><h3>Energy</h3><p>Volatile demand and market signals make assumptions hard to hold.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="ind reveal" data-delay="2">
      <div class="ind-vis"><svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none"><path d="M14 22h36l-3 28H17z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M24 22v-4a8 8 0 0116 0v4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></div>
      <div><span class="mono-tag">FMCG</span><h3>FMCG</h3><p>Fast cycles and promotions drive constant demand volatility.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</HomePanel>
